title: eQ real estate funds acquired properties for 57 million euros (eQ Oyj)
text: ( Source : eQ Oyj) 05/10/ 2015 eQ Asset Management has raised over 300 million euros of equity capital for real estate funds and the total investment capacity of eQ's two real estate funds, Special Investment Fund eQ Finnish Real Estate ( AIF )
